snippet.textDisplay:
Score: Composition 10/10, Singing 10/10, Overall 10/10 Shani's Season Score: B, 3.0/5.

Ah, what a year this was for Coke Studio.  Last nail in the coffin was so wrenching that it has taken back on the evening of June 22, 2016, a man proclaimed dead after taking two bullets in his head and one in ear, was Amjad Sabri and the brutality was at its peak. Who could tell, this was going to be his last performance and performance like this would drenched his family into tears and nation probably. Bu I want those who took his life to look right in his eye and at least ponder what they have done. But no when a man kills man, no integrity is left, this is last a human could do. 

I wan't to thank CS for such a great journey.  This season was one of best if not the best.  Thank you CS.
